txt.en: An undeniable way to confuse and thwart the efforts of the White Hand is to defeat their leader, Nágri, at Fushaum-dorám.
An undeniable way to confuse and thwart the efforts of the White Hand is to defeat their leader, Nágri, at Fushaum-dorám.
Nágri, the leader of the White Hand Orcs in the Writhendowns, can be found at Fushaum-dorám.\n\nYou should find and defeat Nágri.
You have defeated Nágri, the leader of the White Hand Orcs at Fushaum-dorám. Hopefully this will hinder the plans of whatever new assault these Orcs were hatching.
